Model Part Num: 90IG0241-BM3000 :4x 5dBi external antennas {{FCC ST|05/28/2016|indexme.}} ===Specifications=== *802.11ac and concurrent dual-band connectivity delivers up to 1167 Mbps data rate :for smooth streaming 4K videos from Youtube and Netflix *4 fixed 5dBi antennas and beamforming technology strengthens wireless coverage *Multi-purpose USB 2.0 ports for 3G/4G, printer, file sharing and media streaming *Gigabit Ethernet ports for the fastest, most reliable internet performance, especially :UHD gaming and streaming *Set up time restriction & website filtering via parental control function to protect :your children away from potential dangers *ASUSWRT dashboard UI enables setup with robust network monitoring and control ==Links of Interest== [http://www.asus.com/Networking/RT-AC1200G-Plus/specifications/ Specifications] {{â€¢}} [http://www.asus.com/Networking/RT-AC1200G-Plus/gallery/ Gallery] ===Reviews=== *[http://foxnetlab.com/index.php/reviews/16-reviews/171-asus-rt-ac1200g ''ASUS RT-AC1200G+'' on '''FoxNetLab'''] *[http://www.ixbt.com/comm/asus-rt-ac1200gplus.shtml ''ASUS RT-AC1200G+'' on '''iXBT'''] (RU) ===Forum threads=== *[https://forum.openwrt.org/viewtopic.php?id=65275 ''ASUS RT-AC1200G+'' on '''OpenWrt''' forums] *[http://www.dd-wrt.com/phpBB2/viewtopic.php?t=287041 ''ASUS RT-AC1200G+'' on '''DD-WRT''' forums] (cpuinfo) *[https://openitforum.pl/forums/topic/1283-asus-rt-ac1200g/ ''ASUS RT-AC1200G+'' on '''OpenITforum''' forums] (PL) *[http://koolshare.cn/thread-30747-1-1.html ''ASUS RT-AC1200'' on '''KoolShare''' forums] (images PCB) ==JTAG-Serial Info== ===Serial=== {{/Serial info}} [[Category:English Documentation]]
